headline.main: Disgraced Journalist Charged Over Bomb Threats to U.S. Jewish Groups
headline.print_headline: Disgraced Journalist Charged Over Bomb Threats to U.S. Jewish Groups

lead_paragraph: Jihadists on motorbikes killed two people including a school official early Friday in a village in Burkina Faso's north and then went to other villages demanding that schools close, a provincial official said.
